I think we both agree that storing passwords in config files is a bad idea, no?
So why do we want to keep introducing (optional) password parameters, following the wrong pattern?

What you propose with HADOOP-15325 is adding an optional option to ignore an optional parameter. Why?, Hi Konstantin, There's probably a misunderstanding here. 

